products.title: ASUS GeForce RTX 2060 6G Turbo Edition GDDR6 HDMI DP 1.4 Graphics Card (TURBO RTX2060-6G)
features: Powered by NVIDIA Turing with 1710 MHz Boost Clock (OC Mode), 1920 CUDA cores and 6GB GDDR6 memory
Supports up-to 4 monitors with DisplayPort 1. 4 and HDMI 2. 0 Ports
8mm dual-ball Bearing fans and cutting-edge shroud provide superior cooing and Airflow, All while being quiet, efficient, and having 2x the lifespan compared to traditional Sleeve bearing fans.
144 Hour validation program ensures the best stability of your GPU through rigorous and extensive testing with heavy workloads.
Gpu Tweak II makes monitoring performance and streaming in real time easier than ever, and includes additional software like Game Booster, split Game caster, WT Fast and Quantum Cloud
products.description: Experience Turing Triple Threat with ASUS TURBO RTX 2060-6G. The ASUS TURBO RTX 2060 6G features a new cutting edge cooling shroud for multi-card configurations and small chassis, Dual-Ball Bearing Fan with IP5X Dust resistance, and easy overclocking and monitoring with the intuitive GPU Tweak II software. Recommended PSU: 500W.
